title: E386 Sean O'Malley & Tim Welch
itunes:title: Sean O'Malley & Tim Welch
description:
Sean O'Malley is a mixed martial artist who currently competes in the bantamweight division of the UFC. Tim Welch is a mixed martial artists, trainer, and coach. Find them together on the Timbo Sugar Show.

Theo, Sean, and Tim discuss the Oscars slap heard 'round the world, open relationships, Colby/Masvidal beef, and Sean's upcoming fight plans.

Find Sean: https://www.instagram.com/sugaseanmma/?hl=en

Find Tim: https://www.instagram.com/timwelchmt/?hl=en
